main event: Three rectangular shaped objects were observed in the sky over Zonguldak, Turkey, on 25 October 1955.
interesting points: The objects appeared and disappeared at intervals of 10-15 seconds.,The sighting lasted for a total of 45 minutes.,The report indicates multiple sources witnessed the event.,The aircraft was present during the sighting.,The objects were seen over water at a height of 5000-10000 ft.
